against me.

27:44.790 --> 27:46.018
And you.

27:46.060 --> 27:48.790
And I won't stand
beside you.

27:48.830 --> 27:52.129
Not again, Peter.

27:52.170 --> 27:54.468
Not in a million years.

27:54.500 --> 27:57.139
So... don't listen to me,

27:57.170 --> 28:00.003
keep lying to me,
I don't care.

28:00.040 --> 28:02.736
But_|i_sten_ to_
your political instincts.

28:02.780 --> 28:04.145
