28:31.170 --> 28:33.206
I... like your
hair that way.

28:33.240 --> 28:35.037
I do, too.
Let's do it now.

28:35.080 --> 28:37.105
All right, you heard her!
Let's go, come on!

28:39.050 --> 28:40.142
ALICIA:
I was shocked.

28:40.180 --> 28:41.249
I wasn't _used
to politics,

28:41.280 --> 28:42.440
and suddenly I was forced

28:42.480 --> 28:43.845
into the middle of it.

28:43.890 --> 28:46.415
With my husband in prison,

28:46.450 --> 28:47.986
what could I do?

28:48.020 --> 28:50.056
I went back to work.

28:50.090 --> 28:52.957
I had to work harder
than anybody

28:52.990 --> 28:54.423
and then I had to go home

28:54.460 --> 28:56.348
and hold my kids.

28:56.400 --> 28:59.324
I got the call at a speech

28:59.370 --> 29:01.395
I was giving for Peter.

29:02.870 --> 29:04.838
My friend was dead.

29:04.870 --> 29:08.101
Will Gardner hired me

29:08.140 --> 29:10.506
when no one else would.

29:11.880 --> 29:15.475
