JOSH: We tried

31:33.350 --> 31:34.612
dark, too.
(Alicia sighs)

31:34.660 --> 31:36.287
Damn, I have to redo

31:36.320 --> 31:37.924
this interview.
Which is too bad,

31:37.960 --> 31:39.985
'cause it was great.
Can you get it back?

31:40.030 --> 31:41.691
