31:41.730 --> 31:43.527
I'll go change.

31:44.570 --> 31:47.323
Well, I was shocked.

31:47.370 --> 31:48.689
Terribly shocked.

31:48.740 --> 31:51.004
Politics was new to me,

31:51.040 --> 31:54.134
and suddenly
there was this scandal.

31:54.180 --> 31:56.000
And then I had to be home

31:56.040 --> 31:57.632
with my kids.
"Had to be"?

31:57.680 --> 32:01.172
It sounds like
a punishment.
Right.

32:03.150 --> 32:04.549
I was shocked.

32:04.590 --> 32:06.387
Truly, truly shocked.

32:06.420 --> 32:08.559
Terribly shocked.

32:08.590 --> 32:10.148
I know.
I got this.

32:10.190 --> 32:12.181
Mm-hmm.
Just wait.
(clears throat)

32:15.400 --> 32:17.356
I was shocked.

32:17.400 --> 32:21.268
All I could think about was
my kids, being home with them.

32:22.440 --> 32:24.431
Which I wanted to be...

32:24.470 --> 32:27.007
because...

32:27.040 --> 32:29.702
child services said I had to.
(groans)

32:29.740 --> 32:32.049
I know._
Just... wait.

32:32.080 --> 32:33.308
(clears throat)

32:33.350 --> 32:35.318
Well, I was shocked
at the scandal.

32:35.350 --> 32:37.568
Politics was new to me...

32:37.620 --> 32:39.986
