32:44.460 --> 32:46.587
Okay. Shake it off.

32:46.630 --> 32:49.326
Right. Yeah. I know.
Just do it

32:49.360 --> 32:51.464
like you did
it before.

32:51.500 --> 32:53.195
(sniffles)

32:54.370 --> 32:56.190
I'm sorry.

32:56.240 --> 32:58.333
(sniffles)
No. I'm sorry.

32:58.370 --> 33:00.258
I hate being
the cause of this.

33:00.310 --> 33:03.199
You're not the cause.

33:03.240 --> 33:04.741
I should resign.
No.

33:04.780 --> 33:06.509
Could you
please pull over?

33:06.550 --> 33:08.518
Ramona, Ramona, wait.

33:22.700 --> 33:25.260
We're bad people.

33:27.330 --> 33:29.298
I know.

33:45.450 --> 33:47.441
I need to stop being afraid.

33:47.490 --> 33:49.481
Do you have an opinion
on that?

33:51.490 --> 33:53.720
People sometimes have
a reason to be afraid.

33:53.760 --> 33:57.355
Do I?

33:57.400 --> 33:58.822
I don't know.

33:58.870 --> 34:02.135
My worry is fear is creating
the reason to be afraid.

34:02.170 --> 34:04.809
I don't have an opinion
about that.

34:04.840 --> 34:07.502
I need to talk
to Bishop.

34:07.540 --> 34:10.771
Look, I don't think
that's a good idea.

34:10.810 --> 34:13.301
Phone Kalinda first.

34:14.720 --> 34:16.608
You said "phone"--
phone Kalinda?

34:16.650 --> 34:17.844
Yeah.

34:17.880 --> 34:19.484
Most people in America,
they say "call."

34:19.520 --> 34:20.487
Did you know that?

34:20.520 --> 34:21.589
Makes sense.

34:21.620 --> 34:23.258
You call someone.

34:23.290 --> 34:24.757
Right, Bishop said "call."
In reception, he said,

34:24.790 --> 34:25.779
"I guess I should've called."

34:25.830 --> 34:27.127
Okay.

34:27.160 --> 34:28.297
On the wiretap,
he said "phone."

34:28.330 --> 34:30.093
"Phone me when you have a plan."

34:30.130 --> 34:31.097
I didn't hear it.

34:31.130 --> 34:32.097
He said "phone."

34:32.130 --> 34:33.427
Mm, people say both.

34:33.470 --> 34:35.165
No, not usually.

34:35.200 --> 34:37.361
Are we betting
your life on "usually"?

34:37.400 --> 34:39.630
I've been betting my life
on a lot less these days.

34:39.670 --> 34:41.228
I'm not a gambler,
but it's amazing

34:41.280 --> 34:42.429
how prison
makes you one.

34:42.480 --> 34:44.368
What are you doing?

34:44.410 --> 34:45.638
I'm going to
see Bishop.

34:45.680 --> 34:46.669
That's not smart.

34:46.710 --> 34:47.870
Bishop saw you.

34:47.910 --> 34:49.309
He thinks I turned against him.

34:49.350 --> 34:51.409
I need to convince him
that I haven't.

34:51.450 --> 34:53.418
I need to do this.

