of you threatening to kill me.

39:31.570 --> 39:34.539
And I came here without
a bodyguard to tell you

39:34.570 --> 39:36.367
I am not a threat to you.

39:37.640 --> 39:39.005
When did they
play this?

39:39.040 --> 39:41.008
Two days ago.

39:41.040 --> 39:43.008
And you believed it?

39:43.040 --> 39:46.703
I thought it was fake,
but I wasn't sure.

39:46.750 --> 39:48.741
Is it faked?

39:51.790 --> 39:53.018
No.

39:58.590 --> 40:00.888
I talk, Cary.

40:00.930 --> 40:02.750
I talk all the time.

40:02.800 --> 40:06.065
I say things
I don't mean.

40:06.100 --> 40:09.069
I'm sure you say things
you don't mean, too.

40:09.100 --> 40:10.829
Sometimes.

40:12.110 --> 40:15.637
