No, I won't. Ever.

40:32.190 --> 40:33.555
Good.

40:33.590 --> 40:35.592
Then I have no
issue With you.

40:37.230 --> 40:39.198
The bodyguard
had me worried.

40:39.230 --> 40:41.198
Well, it wasn't my idea.

40:41.230 --> 40:43.790
Good.

40:43.840 --> 40:45.728
Then that's that.

40:48.910 --> 40:51.208
Dylan wanted me to play.

40:53.150 --> 40:55.141
I'll tell him
you had to go.

40:57.780 --> 41:00.180
Cary.

41:02.520 --> 41:03.919
Don't hurt me...

41:05.190 --> 41:07.181
...and I won't hurt you.

