You're good? Meaning you're
not in the house anymore?

41:15.940 --> 41:17.168
Yeah, I'm in the car.

41:17.200 --> 41:18.906
Bishop didn't try anything?

41:18.940 --> 41:21.158
No, we talked.
Everything's good.

41:21.210 --> 41:23.906
So he didn't say it?

41:23.940 --> 41:25.646
The tape wasn't him?

41:25.680 --> 41:27.671
No, it was him,
but he didn't mean it.

41:29.650 --> 41:31.049
What the hell, Cary?

41:31.080 --> 41:33.913
I have to go.

41:47.100 --> 41:49.091
I take you seriously.

41:51.240 --> 41:55.028
It's not
easy, but...

41:55.080 --> 41:57.105
I take you seriously.

42:03.080 --> 42:04.809
Good.

